author: Nerdstalgic
description:
In 1976, Sylvester Stallone became a Hollywood icon by bringing Rocky Balboa to life. The underdog story captured audiences worldwide, launching a franchise that made Stallone a powerhouse in the industry.  Decades later, the Creed films breathed new life into the Rocky saga, introducing a new generation to the franchise. But when Creed III hit theaters, fans were shocked to see Rocky Balboa was nowhere to be found.

title: The REAL Reason Rocky Balboa Isn't In Creed III
